OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,FA woman with MS feels like her "life
OL,7,Fis being played with" after still not
OL,8,Fhaving access to a potentially life-
OL,9,Fimproving drug, four years after it
OL,10,Fwas made available on the NHS in Wales.
OL,12,FToday the Public Services Ombudsman
OL,13,Ffor Wales has criticised Aneurin Bevan
OL,14,FUniversity Health Board for its
OL,15,Ffailure to offer fampridine to any
OL,16,Feligible patients. It is estimated
OL,17,Faround 500 people in the health
OL,18,Fboard's area are eligible for the drug.
