OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,FThe drug was approved for use within
OL,7,FNHS Wales at the end of 2019 and it
OL,8,Fhas been found to improve walking for
OL,9,Fsome patients with the condition,
OL,10,Fwhich affects mobility.
OL,12,FThe ombudsman's investigation was
OL,13,Ftriggered following a complaint by a
OL,14,F57-year-old patient identified as Mrs
OL,15,FX who was diagnosed with MS in 2009
OL,16,Fand has been in the secondary
OL,17,Fprogressive stage of the disease for
OL,18,Froughly ten years.
