OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,FThe Health Board said it had been
OL,7,Funable to offer the drug due to a lack
OL,8,Fof resources. It said that a business
OL,9,Fcase for the introduction of the drug
OL,10,Fwas being developed, including the
OL,11,Fneed to recruit suitable staff to
OL,12,Fensure the safe roll-out of fampridine
OL,13,Ftreatment.
