OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,FIt also said it was not able to refer
OL,7,Fpatients to other health boards
OL,8,Fnearby, as they already had waiting
OL,9,Flists for accessing fampridine within
OL,10,Ftheir own areas. Fampridine is not
OL,11,FNHSfunded in England, so the Health
OL,12,FBoard stated there was no possibility
OL,13,Fof seeking an agreement to refer
OL,14,Fpatients there for treatment.
OL,16,FPublic Services Ombudsman for Wales,
OL,17,FMichelle Morris, said: "Newly approved
OL,18,Fmedicines should be offered within 60
OL,19,Fdays of approval by the Welsh
OL,20,FGovernment.
