OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,F"It is therefore concerning that
OL,7,Ffampridine is not being offered to any
OL,8,Fof the eligible patients within the
OL,9,FHealth Board's area.
OL,11,F"Even if the Health Board's own Pre-
OL,12,FInvestment Panel approves the funding
OL,13,Fimmediately, the Health Board has
OL,14,Festimated another 3 to 6 months to
OL,15,Frecruit staff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
