OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,F"This means that the earliest
OL,7,Ffampridine could be offered to
OL,8,Fpatients is the middle of 2024. This
OL,9,Frepresents over 4 years since the
OL,10,Fapproval of fampridine as an NHS-
OL,11,Ffunded treatment in Wales."
OL,13,FShe added: "This delay is
OL,14,Funacceptable. It has caused and
OL,15,Fcontinues to cause injustice to Mrs X,
OL,16,Fand other patients, who remain unclear
OL,17,Fas to when or if they will have access
OL,18,Fto this potentially life-improving
OL,19,Fmedication."
