OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman has made a number of
OL,7,Frecommendations, including that the
OL,8,FHealth Board should apologise to Mrs X
OL,9,Fand that it should urgently establish
OL,10,Fan action plan, with timescales, for
OL,11,Fthe provision of fampridine.
OL,13,FShe also asked the Health Board to
OL,14,Fshare her report with the Board or
OL,15,Frelevant committee who should oversee
OL,16,Fand regularly review the action plan
OL,17,Fto ensure that good progress is made
OL,18,Fand that the actions are completed.
