OL,3,C'My life is being played with': Woman
OL,4,Cwith MS not offered drug
OL,6,FAneurin Bevan University Health Board
OL,7,Fhas accepted the ombudsman's findings
OL,8,Fand agreed to implement its
OL,9,Frecommendations.
OL,11,FA spokesperson told ITV Wales: "We are
OL,12,Fvery sorry for Mrs X's experience and
OL,13,Fwill be contacting her to apologise
OL,14,Ffor the distress this must have caused
OL,15,Fher.
OL,17,F"We are currently working through a
OL,18,Fplan to see how we can meet the
OL,19,FOmbudsman's recommendations in
OL,20,Frelation to the introduction of
OL,21,Ffampridine in our Health Board area."
